# ============================================================================
# TRACKER SPREADSHEET CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================================
# 
# Add these variables to your existing .env file to enable click tracking.
# See CLICK_TRACKING_SYSTEM.md for complete setup instructions.
#
# ============================================================================

# Tracker Spreadsheet ID (central click tracking spreadsheet)
# Get this from the spreadsheet URL:
# https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/[THIS_PART_IS_THE_ID]/edit
TRACKER_SPREADSHEET_ID=1_T9MOTutM_ZJCSkHLmns2Tc5SDVabE25MviGDESaxn8

# Google Apps Script Web App URL (deployed from Tracker spreadsheet)
# Format: https://script.google.com/macros/s/[DEPLOYMENT_ID]/exec
# Get this after deploying the Apps Script web app
# IMPORTANT: Include /exec at the end, no query parameters
TRACKER_DEPLOYMENT_BASE_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbxYOUR_DEPLOYMENT_ID_HERE/exec

# Secret authentication token for click tracking
# MUST match the TRACKER_TOKEN in Apps Script Script Properties
# Generate using: openssl rand -hex 32
# Example: a8f3d9c2e1b4f7a6d5c9b2e3f1a4d8c7b6e2f9a3d4c5b8e1f2a7d6c9b3e4f5a1
TRACKER_TOKEN=your_secret_token_here

# ============================================================================
# SETUP CHECKLIST
# ============================================================================
#
# □ 1. Deploy Google Apps Script web app (see google_apps_script/DEPLOYMENT.md)
# □ 2. Set TRACKER_TOKEN in Apps Script Script Properties
# □ 3. Copy deployment URL to TRACKER_DEPLOYMENT_BASE_URL above
# □ 4. Use the SAME token for TRACKER_TOKEN in this .env file
# □ 5. Create Docs/Clicks/CountryTotals tabs in Tracker spreadsheet
# □ 6. Run: python -m src.orchestrator --mode weekly
# □ 7. Verify Directory tab was created in Tracker spreadsheet
# □ 8. Test a tracking URL by clicking it in Canada/UK/US spreadsheet
# □ 9. Verify click was logged in Tracker->Clicks tab
# □ 10. Verify CountryTotals was updated
#
# ============================================================================
